Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Ike has expressed his desire to have sex in the ‘Pepper dem’ edition of the reality television show. The BBNaija housemate said he was ready to have sex with his love interest, Mercy. Ike made the disclosure during a conversation with Mercy last night. In the heat of the discussion, Ike also expressed his love for Mercy, saying he loves her more than anyone he ever met. According to Ike: “I want you so bad. I love you so much more than anyone I ever loved. “And you know I won’t force you. I want to f*ck you so bad. This d*ck is so big. Eja nla!” Recall that Ike had recently threatened to deal with any male housemate that tries to get close to Mercy if he’s evicted on Sunday.  Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.